[There is a correction of this report: Pseudorabies (Aujeszky's disease) - Finland: (NK) wild boar, OIE, corr 20190927.6698218. The "Diagnostic test results" section in the report below indicates that the wild boar test was positive to real-time PCR. This is in error; the wild boar test was negative to real-time PCR. ProMED apologizes for this mistake. - Mod.CRD]

